#8 Gemini→GPT-4o→本地 SD 三层 Fallback --- P2

**AI2U 教训 L5：**AI2U 采用 Gemini + ChatGPT 双模型切换。DeskBuddy
可以做得更彻底------三层 fallback 含本地降级。

8.1 Circuit Breaker 模式

> // src-tauri/src/ai/circuit_breaker.rs
>
> pub struct CircuitBreaker {
>
> state: Mutex\<BreakerState\>,
>
> failure_threshold: u32, // 连续失败 N 次后断开
>
> recovery_timeout: Duration, // 断开后多久尝试恢复
>
> }
>
> #\[derive(Debug)\]
>
> enum BreakerState {
>
> Closed { consecutive_failures: u32 }, // 正常
>
> Open { opened_at: Instant }, // 断开
>
> HalfOpen, // 试探
>
> }
>
> impl CircuitBreaker {
>
> pub fn can_execute(&self) -\> bool {
>
> let state = self.state.lock().unwrap();
>
> match &\*state {
>
> BreakerState::Closed { .. } =\> true,
>
> BreakerState::Open { opened_at } =\> {
>
> opened_at.elapsed() \> self.recovery_timeout
>
> }
>
> BreakerState::HalfOpen =\> true,
>
> }
>
> }
>
> pub fn record_success(&self) { /\* → Closed { failures: 0 } \*/ }
>
> pub fn record_failure(&self) { /\* failures++ → Open if threshold \*/
> }
>
> }

8.2 三层 Fallback 编排

> // src-tauri/src/ai/fallback_chain.rs
>
> pub struct FallbackChain {
>
> layers: Vec\<FallbackLayer\>,
>
> }
>
> struct FallbackLayer {
>
> provider: Box\<dyn AiProvider\>,
>
> breaker: CircuitBreaker,
>
> priority: u8, // 0 = 最高优先
>
> }
>
> impl FallbackChain {
>
> pub fn new() -\> Self {
>
> Self {
>
> layers: vec\![
>
> FallbackLayer {
>
> provider: Box::new(GeminiFlashProvider::new()),
>
> breaker: CircuitBreaker::new(3, Duration::from_secs(60)),
>
> priority: 0,
>
> },
>
> FallbackLayer {
>
> provider: Box::new(Gpt4oProvider::new()),
>
> breaker: CircuitBreaker::new(3, Duration::from_secs(120)),
>
> priority: 1,
>
> },
>
> FallbackLayer {
>
> provider: Box::new(LocalSdProvider::new()),
>
> breaker: CircuitBreaker::new(5, Duration::from_secs(300)),
>
> priority: 2,
>
> },
>
> \]
>
> }
>
> }
>
> pub async fn complete(&self, req: &AiRequest) -\> Result\<AiResponse\>
> {
>
> let mut last_error = None;
>
> for layer in &self.layers {
>
> if !layer.breaker.can_execute() {
>
> log::info!(\"{} circuit open, skipping\",
>
> layer.provider.name());
>
> continue;
>
> }
>
> if !layer.provider.is_available() {
>
> continue;
>
> }
>
> match layer.provider.complete(req).await {
>
> Ok(resp) =\> {
>
> layer.breaker.record_success();
>
> if layer.priority \> 0 {
>
> log::warn!(
>
> \"Used fallback provider: {}\",
>
> layer.provider.name()
>
> );
>
> }
>
> return Ok(resp);
>
> }
>
> Err(e) =\> {
>
> layer.breaker.record_failure();
>
> log::error!(
>
> \"{} failed: {}\", layer.provider.name(), e
>
> );
>
> last_error = Some(e);
>
> }
>
> }
>
> }
>
> Err(last_error.unwrap_or_else(\|\|
>
> anyhow::anyhow!(\"All providers unavailable\")
>
> ))
>
> }
>
> }

8.3 本地 Stable Diffusion 降级方案

作为最后一层 fallback，本地 SD
不需要网络，但质量和速度会降级。两种实现路径：

  ----------- ----------------------------- -----------------------------
  **方案**    **A: 内嵌 sdcpp (Rust FFI)**  **B: 本地 ComfyUI Server**

  集成方式    stable-diffusion.cpp 编译为   用户本地安装 ComfyUI，Tauri
              Rust crate，内嵌到 Tauri      通过 HTTP 调用 localhost
              binary                        

  优势        零配置，用户无感知            灵活，可用各种模型/LoRA

  劣势        包体积大 (+500MB\~1GB)，需要  用户要手动安装 ComfyUI
              GPU                           

  推荐        Phase 6+ 考虑，当前优先级低   B2B 场景可以推荐这个方案 ✅
  ----------- ----------------------------- -----------------------------

> // src-tauri/src/ai/local_sd.rs
>
> pub struct LocalSdProvider {
>
> comfyui_url: String, // \"http://127.0.0.1:8188\"
>
> client: reqwest::Client,
>
> }
>
> impl LocalSdProvider {
>
> fn is_available(&self) -\> bool {
>
> // 健康检查: ComfyUI 是否在运行
>
> self.client.get(&format!(\"{}/system_stats\", self.comfyui_url))
>
> .send().await.is_ok()
>
> }
>
> async fn complete(&self, req: &AiRequest) -\> Result\<AiResponse\> {
>
> // 将 skin gen prompt 转换为 ComfyUI workflow
>
> let workflow = self.build_workflow(req);
>
> let resp = self.client
>
> .post(&format!(\"{}/prompt\", self.comfyui_url))
>
> .json(&workflow)
>
> .send().await?;
>
> // 轮询结果\...
>
> let images = self.poll_result(resp).await?;
>
> Ok(AiResponse {
>
> content: self.images_to_skin_json(images),
>
> provider: \"local-sd\".into(),
>
> ..Default::default()
>
> })
>
> }
>
> }

